[2;36m                    [0m         ===[33mIssue[0m===                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ERROR: libFuzzer: timeout                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mReport[0m===                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         # Evaluation Report                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Summary                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The issue reports a libFuzzer timeout error, indicating that the fuzzing process    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         exceeded its allocated time limit while testing a particular input or code path.    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         This suggests the presence of code that causes excessive execution time,            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         potentially leading to a Denial of Service [1m([0mDoS[1m)[0m vulnerability or performance       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         degradation in production environments.                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Description                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### What the Issue Is                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The error [32m"libFuzzer: timeout"[0m occurs when libFuzzer, a coverage-guided fuzzing     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         engine, detects that the execution of a test case has exceeded the configured       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         timeout threshold. This timeout mechanism is designed to identify inputs that cause [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         the program to hang, enter infinite loops, or execute computationally expensive     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         operations that take an unreasonable amount of time to complete.                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Vulnerability Type                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         This issue indicates a potential **algorithmic complexity vulnerability** or        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         **Denial of Service [1m([0mDoS[1m)[0m** condition. When specific inputs trigger code paths with [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         poor time complexity or resource management, attackers could exploit this behavior  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         to:                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Cause service unavailability by submitting crafted inputs                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Consume excessive CPU resources                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Degrade system performance                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         - Create hanging processes that require manual intervention                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Important Observations                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. **Reproducibility**: The timeout occurs consistently with certain                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         fuzzer-generated inputs, suggesting a deterministic code path issue rather than     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         random environmental factors.                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. **Execution Time**: The code execution time for problematic inputs exceeds the   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         fuzzer's timeout threshold, which is typically set to detect abnormally             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         long-running operations [1m([0mcommonly configured between [1;36m1[0m-[1;36m60[0m seconds[1m)[0m.                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. **Coverage-Guided Discovery**: Since libFuzzer uses coverage-guided fuzzing, it  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         likely discovered this timeout while exploring specific code branches or            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         combinations of operations that weren't adequately tested with typical inputs.      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ### Parts of the Codebase to Investigate                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         To gain a holistic understanding of this issue, the following areas should be       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         investigated:                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m. **Input Processing Logic**: Examine how the codebase parses and validates input  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         data, particularly:                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Input size handling and bounds checking                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Recursive operations that depend on input-controlled parameters                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Loop constructs where iteration counts are influenced by input values          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m. **Algorithmic Complexity**: Review algorithms in the execution path for:         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Operations with quadratic [1m([0m[1;35mO[0m[1m([0mn²[1m)[0m[1m)[0m or higher complexity                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Nested loops where both dimensions depend on input                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Recursive functions without proper depth limiting                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Backtracking algorithms without pruning mechanisms                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m. **Resource-Intensive Operations**: Investigate areas involving:                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - String manipulation and concatenation in loops                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Regular expression matching with complex patterns                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Memory allocation patterns that could cause excessive garbage collection       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - File I/O or network operations without timeouts                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m. **State Management**: Check for:                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Infinite loop conditions                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Deadlock scenarios in concurrent code                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - State machines with cycles that lack exit conditions                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Retry mechanisms without backoff or maximum attempt limits                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m. **Data Structure Operations**: Analyze:                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Collection resizing and reallocation patterns                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Search operations on unsorted data                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Hash table operations with poor hash distribution                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Tree operations on unbalanced structures                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m. **Fuzzer Artifacts**: Examine:                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - The specific input that triggered the timeout [1m([0mif available in fuzzer          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         artifacts[1m)[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Code coverage reports to identify which branches were exercised                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Execution traces or profiling data showing where time is spent                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m. **Historical Context**: Review:                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Recent code changes that might have introduced the issue                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Related bug reports or performance issues                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m            - Previous fuzzing runs to determine if this is a regression                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         The investigation should focus on identifying code paths where execution time grows [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         disproportionately with input characteristics, particularly where input-controlled  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         values affect loop iterations, recursion depth, or the size of data structures      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         being processed.                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ## Initial Issue Log                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m880[0m[39m:                [0m[1;35mSystem.arraycopy[0m[1;39m([0m[39m keyw, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, strmBuf, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, charMatchCount [0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m881[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m            [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m882[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m883[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m this writes a lonely CR or drops trailing CR LF and LF[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m884[0m[39m:        return [0m[1;35mout.calculateLength[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m885[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis Summary[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe libFuzzer timeout is caused by multiple algorithmic complexity vulnerabilities [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39min the PDFBox PDF parser. The code lacks proper bounds checking on input-controlled[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations, allowing maliciously crafted or fuzzer-generated PDFs to trigger [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpensive operations that exceed timeout thresholds.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Critical Root Causes Identified[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **BruteForceParser byte-by-byte scanning** - Scans entire files without size [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Unbounded string parsing** - No maximum length checks for PDF strings[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Input-controlled xref iteration** - User-controlled loop counts without [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mvalidation[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Missing stream length limits** - Reads until marker found with no size cap[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Validation cascade triggering full file scans** - Failed validation triggers [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpensive brute force[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Add Constant Definitions for Size Limits[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.java` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m65[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd the following constants following the existing pattern of [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`OBJECT_NUMBER_THRESHOLD`, `GENERATION_NUMBER_THRESHOLD`, and `MAX_LENGTH_LONG`:[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_ARRAY_ELEMENTS = 100_000;[0m                              [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final long MAX_STREAM_LENGTH = 100_000_000; [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m 100MB[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/XrefParser.java` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mafter imports[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix [0m[1;35mparseCOSString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to Prevent Unbounded String Parsing[0m                     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After each [0m[1;35mout.write[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, increment:[0m                                               [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis approach limits the count rather than rejecting the file, maintaining [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompatibility while preventing timeout.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        lastEOFMarker, MAX_FILE_SIZE_FOR_BF_SEARCH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis prevents brute force scanning on large files while allowing normal xref-based [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m7[0m[39m. Fix [0m[1;35mfindString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to Add Maximum Search Distance[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BruteForceParser.java` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m780[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m809[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modification:** Track bytes read and limit search distance:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After line [0m[1;36m784[0m[39m where counter is initialized, add: `long bytesSearched = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside the while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m786[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, increment counter and check limit:[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After line [0m[1;36m786[0m[39m, before line [0m[1;36m788[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytesSearched++;[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytesSearched > MAX_SEARCH_DISTANCE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Search distance exceeded maximum [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m bytes, string not found"[0m[39m, [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        MAX_SEARCH_DISTANCE[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    return -1L;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m. Fix [0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to Limit Element Count[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.java` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m755[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m822[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modification:** Add element count validation:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside the while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m763[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Before adding element to array [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbefore line [0m[1;36m814[0m[1;39m)[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add check:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Before line [0m[1;36m814[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpo.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= MAX_ARRAY_ELEMENTS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Array element count exceeds maximum [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m at offset [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, truncating"[0m[39m, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        MAX_ARRAY_ELEMENTS, [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    break;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m9[0m[39m. Fix [0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to Limit Entry Count[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/BaseParser.java` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m281[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m328[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modification:** Track dictionary size and enforce limit:[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Inside the while loop [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m288[0m[1;39m)[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After successful name-value pair parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter line [0m[1;36m300[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add check:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After line [0m[1;36m303[0m[39m, before continuing loop[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mobj.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m >= MAX_DICT_ENTRIES[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Dictionary entry count exceeds maximum [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m at offset [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, truncating"[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        MAX_DICT_ENTRIES, [0m[1;35msource.getPosition[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    break;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m. Add Safety Check in [0m[1;35mcheckXrefOffsets[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location:** `pdfbox/src/main/java/org/apache/pdfbox/pdfparser/XrefParser.java` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m445[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m459[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Modification:** Add file size check before triggering brute force:[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After line [0m[1;36m448[0m[39m where validation returns false[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Before line [0m[1;36m450[0m[39m where brute force parser is invoked[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Add conditional check:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m After line [0m[1;36m448[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;35mvalidateXrefOffsets[0m[1;39m([0m[39mxrefOffset[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Only trigger brute force for reasonably sized files[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m <= MAX_FILE_SIZE_FOR_BF_SEARCH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        Map<COSObjectKey, Long> bfCOSObjectKeyOffsets = [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mparser.getBruteForceParser[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35m.getBFCOSObjectOffsets[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m [0m[33m...[0m[39m rest of existing code[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m else [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"File size [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m exceeds maximum for brute force search, "[0m[39m +[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"proceeding with potentially incomplete xref table"[0m[39m, [0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mNote: Need to verify that `[0m[1;35msource.length[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method exists or use `fileLen` field [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfrom COSParser.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification and Rationale[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Approach is Optimal[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Follows Existing Patterns**: The fix strategy uses the same defensive [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprogramming patterns already present in the codebase [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`OBJECT_NUMBER_THRESHOLD`, `MAX_LENGTH_LONG`, `readStringNumber` validation[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Minimal Invasiveness**: Changes are localized to specific parsing methods [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout altering the overall architecture or API surface.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Graceful Degradation**: Most limits log warnings and truncate data rather than[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfailing completely, maintaining compatibility with edge-case PDFs while preventing [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDoS.[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Configurable Limits**: Constants can be adjusted based on real-world [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mrequirements without code changes.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Defense in Depth**: Multiple layers of protection ensure that even if one [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck is bypassed, others will catch problematic inputs.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Preserves Existing Logic[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **No Fuzzing Code Modification**: All changes are in the core PDF parsing logic,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnot in any harness or test code.[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Maintains PDF Spec Compliance**: Limits are set high enough to handle [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlegitimate PDFs while blocking malicious inputs.[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves Lenient Mode**: The parser still attempts to handle malformed PDFs [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut with safety guardrails.[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **No API Changes**: Public interfaces remain unchanged; all modifications are [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minternal.[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Backward Compatible**: Legitimate PDFs that respect reasonable size limits [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwill parse identically.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Timeout Issues[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Prevents Unbounded Loops**: Every input-controlled loop now has a maximum [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration count or accumulated size limit.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Blocks Expensive Brute Force**: File size checks prevent byte-by-byte scanning[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mof large files.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Limits Memory Allocation**: String and array size limits prevent excessive [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory growth.[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Breaks Timeout Cascades**: Validation failures no longer automatically trigger[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexpensive full-file scans.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Maintains Performance**: Buffered reading and existing optimizations are [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreserved.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Legitimate large PDFs might be truncated**[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Mitigation: Limits are set to very large values [0m[1;39m([0m[39m10MB strings, [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m array [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39melements, 1M xref entries[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Real-world PDFs rarely exceed these limits[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Log warnings provide visibility when limits are hit[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Some corrupted PDFs might fail to parse that previously [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msucceeded**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Mitigation: Brute force is only disabled for files >10MB[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Most corrupted PDFs are small test cases or malicious inputs[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Lenient mode still attempts recovery within limits[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Side Effect [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Performance impact from additional checks**[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Mitigation: Checks are simple comparisons with negligible overhead[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Only performed in hot loops that are already I/O bound[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Net performance improvement by preventing worst-case scenarios[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Reference to Similar Solutions[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe `PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH` pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39mfontbox, line [0m[1;36m71[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m demonstrates the same [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapproach:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Defines reasonable maximum size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m100MB for font data[0m[1;39m)[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Checks accumulated size before allocation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m162[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m164[0m[1;39m)[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throws IOException when exceeded[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This pattern is proven effective in the same codebase[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe `[0m[1;35mreadStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` validation [0m[1;39m([0m[39mBaseParser, lines [0m[1;36m1450[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1454[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m shows existing [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39macceptance of this pattern:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Checks buffer length in loop[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Throws IOException with descriptive message[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Already protects against unbounded number parsing[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Implementation Priority[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Phase [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mCritical - Immediate[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mbfSearchForObjects[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - file size check[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mfindString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - search distance limit[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseCOSString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - string length limit[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseXrefTable[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - xref count validation[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Phase [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mHigh - Soon[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mreadUntilEndStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - stream length limit[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mcheckXrefOffsets[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - brute force trigger guard[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseCOSArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - array size limit[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Phase [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMedium - Follow-up[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:**[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m8[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseCOSDictionary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - dictionary size limit[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m9[0m[39m. Fix `[0m[1;35mparseCOSHexString[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - hex string length limit[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m10[0m[39m. Add recursion depth tracking [0m[1;39m([0m[39mif needed after testing[0m[1;39m)[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis prioritization addresses the most critical timeout sources first while [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaintaining a structured rollout.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
